Samuel Ortom, govenor of Benue state, on Tuesday, visited former President Goodluck Jonathan. The meeting was held at the residence of the former president in Abuja. According to a statement by Nathaniel Ikyur, chief press secretary to Ortom, the meeting was held “in a bid to strengthen the PDP family ahead of the 2023 general elections”. Ortom was the minister of state, trade and investment under the administration of Jonathan. See photos below. <img class="alignnone wp-image-700035" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM2.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM2.jpeg 720w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM2-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM2-24x16.jpeg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM2-36x24.jpeg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM2-48x32.jpeg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> <img class="alignnone wp-image-700036" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="418" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM.jpeg 1080w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM-300x228.jpeg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM-1024x778.jpeg 1024w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WhatsApp-Image-2022-05-17-at-12.31.37-PM-768x584.jpeg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uplo